{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "b357732e-1465-405a-9cde-5a5d15893f7b",
    "name": "Anime Management API",
    "description": "API untuk sistem manajemen anime dengan fitur CRUD data master (Anime, Genres, Users), CRUD data transaksional (Reviews, Watchlists), dan Statistik.\n\n## Cara Penggunaan\n\nSetiap request menggunakan Base URL:\n\n> {{BASE_URL}}/api \n  \n\n## Environment Variables\n\n- BASE_URL: [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000)\n    \n\n## Endpoint Groups\n\n1. **Anime** - CRUD data anime\n    \n2. **Genres** - CRUD data genre\n    \n3. **Users** - CRUD data user\n    \n4. **Reviews** - CRUD data review\n    \n5. **Watchlists** - CRUD data watchlist\n    \n6. **Statistics** - Data statistik",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "53758336",
    "_collection_link": "https://go.postman.co/collection/53758336-b357732e-1465-405a-9cde-5a5d15893f7b?source=collection_link"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200 && jsonData.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', jsonData.token);",
                  "    console.log('Token tersimpan:', jsonData.token);",
                  "} else if (pm.response.code !== 200) {",
                  "    console.log('Login gagal:', jsonData.message);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"username\": \"animefan1\",\n    \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": [
                "{{BASE_URL}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "auth",
                "login"
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ],
      "description": "Endpoint autentikasi (tidak perlu token)"
    },
